front.title: H.248 Annex F (Fax, Text Conversation, and Call discrimination))

abstract.t: This document reproduces the content of the ITU-T Study Group 16White Document draft of H.248 Annex F, which was decided in Genevain November 2000. It also includes minor corrections made in January 2001.This document is submitted for IETF in accordance withprocedures currently being negotiated betweenITU-T Study Group and ISOC on behalf of the IETF.
